snippet.title: Funniest, cutest and most amusing ANIMAL videos #4  - Funny animal compilation - Watch & laugh!
snippet.description:
Animals are so sweet, cute and funny! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, fish, whales, squirrels, raccoons, horses, hamsters, monkeys, seals,... behave, play, sleep and snore, fail, make funny sounds, sneeze...! So adorable and hilarious! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
